<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-19 16:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4270 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CHOOSING-COLLEGES-NYT     09-19 0730
