<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-19 18:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4328 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-COMMERCIAL-REAL-825&AMP;A     09-19 0866
