A4342 &Cx1f; ttc-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LADN-SPORTS-BUDGET &LR;      09-19 0351
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LADN-SPORTS-BUDGET </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Sept. 20 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Brad Nelson at (818) 713-3602.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-ANGELS-MARINERS (Anaheim, Calif.) _ The Anaheim Angels face
the Seattle Mariners at 7:05 p.m. PDT.
</P>
<P>
   By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BBA-ANGELNOTES (Anaheim, Calif.) _ Notebook from the
Angels-Mariners game.
</P>
<P>
   By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BBA-MODESTI-COLUMN (Anaheim, Calif.) _ Column from Angels game.
</P>
<P>
   By Kevin Modesti. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-USC (Los Angeles) _ Pac-10 opener: USC vs. Oregon State. 7
p.m. PDT.
</P>
<P>
   By Scott Wolf. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-CROUSE-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ From USC game.
</P>
<P>
   By Karen Crouse. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-UCLA (Houston) _ UCLA vs. Houston.
</P>
<P>
